  "keyFeatures": [
    "Offline Speech-to-Text with multiple model types (Zipformer, Paraformer, Whisper, NeMo CTC, etc.)",
    "Online (streaming) Speech-to-Text with real-time recognition and partial results",
    "Text-to-Speech with multiple models (VITS, Matcha, Kokoro, Kitten, etc.)",
    "Streaming Text-to-Speech with incremental generation",
    "Hardware acceleration support (CPU, NNAPI, XNNPACK, Core ML, QNN)",
    "Voice Activity Detection (VAD)",
    "Speaker Diarization",
    "Speech Enhancement and Source Separation",
    "Flexible model loading from assets, file system, or auto-detection",
    "Full TypeScript support with complete type definitions"
